featured_reviews.review_id:
Came to this legendary mosque to attend a friends wedding. Unfortunately the mosque and its facilities (toilets) has been neglected.

This once great mosque that was built for the first lady of the country is now in a monument of what happens if you dont maintain the cleanliness of a building. A place of worship should be clean and pristine.

Hopefully they will restore this once beautiful structure to its glory days.
